headline: ADTRAN Beats Q4 Earnings Estimates on Healthy Revenue Growth
summary: ADTN beats Q4 estimates as revenue jumps on cloud, fiber and AI demand, narrows losses and guides Q1 sales to $275-$295M amid macro risks.
